{"tid":2515651,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"對比起UPRO, VOO有咩優勢","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T07:22:01.000Z","uid":250073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"91b1344e90f71ee9837203272e494c5d00c5f9f8","tid":2515651,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"新手認真一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nUPRO係唔係有啲乜嘢潛在嘅風險或者缺點係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b036c10c510609e43380336f434996968c712928","tid":2515651,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"179af761e84f0396c3497fcdae85b8671cc5c8d2","tid":2515651,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"摸頂入upro，股災你會仆街"},{"pid":"67823fe86120b4ab2b869c7c51b192e277efef50","tid":2515651,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"順埋問埋<br />\nSPLG 點解好似咁少人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都淨係講VOO"},{"pid":"a56ba615f90523a4269a7520bb76f3058076e87a","tid":2515651,"uid":286928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"好：<br />\n唔會爆倉<br />\n提升户口購買力<br />\n長期熊蝕少過孖展<br />\n長期牛會賺得比直接孖展仲多<br />\n<br />\n壞：<br />\n遇上世紀級股災有機會十年甚至永遠返唔到家鄉<br />\n散户只能係部分券商買<br />\n横行市會蝕錢<br />\n<br />\n美股勁所以多數賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過如果係恆指杠杆ETF應該豬死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6dee27bfdd45f59298f20e006d2140414f95b2","tid":2515651,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"唔好講咩橫行市同手續費先<br />\n一個有槓桿 一個無。本身就係唔同選擇黎<br />\n正如你問去買樓。做2成同做五成有咩優勢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284c9d351c36973c3ac1b91547d1571b02a3c274","tid":2515651,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"你睇咗依個post未？<br />\n<br />\n【數學+歷史分析】 Leveraged ETF 可否長揸？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409324</a><br />\n<br />\nLeveraged ETF優點係喺S&amp;P 500連續兩個交易日上升嗰陣，UPRO升幅會高過S&amp;P 500升幅3倍。喺S&amp;P 500連續兩個交易日下跌嗰陣，UPRO跌幅會少過S&amp;P 500跌幅3倍。<br />\n缺點係當S&amp;P 500先升後跌或者先跌後升嗰陣，就算S&amp;P 500無變，UPRO都會輸。假設S&amp;P 500本身4100點，然後先升25%後跌20%，S&amp;P 500會維持不變(4100*1.25*0.8 = 4100)，VOO嘅價格都會差唔多無變。<br />\n不過如果你揸3倍ETF，假設UPRO本身係$100。S&amp;P 500先升25%後跌20%之後UPRO就會變成$100*1.75*0.4 = $70，S&amp;P 500無變，UPRO都會下跌30%。"},{"pid":"d7b5c62f3ce2600425ad18f4c34c5a4d10a5091e","tid":2515651,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"唔係個個rick torlence承受到3倍槓桿 同埋expense ratio高d"},{"pid":"972a384396912224dec1265fa2e43a5ddae5603a","tid":2515651,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67823fe86120b4ab2b869c7c51b192e277efef50","tid":2515651,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"順埋問埋<br />\nSPLG 點解好似咁少人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都淨係講VOO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"因為index fund唔係100%緊貼指數嚟郁，多唔多人買隻fund都會有影響。<br />\n如果某隻fund少人玩，liquidity就會低，咁就會無咁值錢。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"67823fe86120b4ab2b869c7c51b192e277efef50","tid":2515651,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"順埋問埋<br />\nSPLG 點解好似咁少人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都淨係講VOO"}}